---
import Logo from '../assets/logo.webp';
---

<footer class="bg-black border-t border-gray-800 py-12 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8">
      <div class="col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <img src={Logo.src || "/placeholder.svg"} alt="QuickLand Logo" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full mr-3" />
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">QuickLand Network</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">El mejor servidor de Minecraft en español. Únete a nuestra comunidad y vive aventuras épicas.</p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a href="https://discord.quickland.net" target="_blank" class="text-[#7289DA] hover:text-[#5865F2] transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" viewBox="0 0 127.14 96.36" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M107.7 8.07A105.15 105.15 0 0 0 81.47 0a72.06 72.06 0 0 0-3.36 6.83 97.68 97.68 0 0 0-29.11 0A72.37 72.37 0 0 0 45.64 0a105.89 105.89 0 0 0-26.25 8.09C2.79 32.65-1.71 56.6.54 80.21a105.73 105.73 0 0 0 32.17 16.15 77.7 77.7 0 0 0 6.89-11.11 68.42 68.42 0 0 1-10.85-5.18c.91-.66 1.8-1.34 2.66-2a75.57 75.57 0 0 0 64.32 0c.87.71 1.76 1.39 2.66 2a68.68 68.68 0 0 1-10.87 5.19 77 77 0 0 0 6.89 11.1 105.25 105.25 0 0 0 32.19-16.14c2.64-27.38-4.51-51.11-18.9-72.15ZM42.45 65.69C36.18 65.69 31 60 31 53s5-12.74 11.43-12.74S54 46 53.89 53s-5.05 12.69-11.44 12.69Zm42.24 0C78.41 65.69 73.25 60 73.25 53s5-12.74 11.44-12.74S96.23 46 96.12 53s-5.04 12.69-11.43 12.69Z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:quickland36@gmail.com" class="text-[#55ffff] hover:text-[#33cccc] transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Enlaces Rápidos</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
          <li><a href="https://discord.quickland.net" target="_blank" class="hover:text-[#55ffff] transition-colors">Discord</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://tienda.quickland.net" target="_blank" class="hover:text-[#55ffff] transition-colors">Tienda</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:quickland36@gmail.com" class="hover:text-[#55ffff] transition-colors">Soporte</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-white font-semibold mb-4">Información</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
          <li>Java: quickland.net</li>
          <li>Bedrock: bedrock.quickland.net:19132</li>
          <li>Versión: 1.8 - 1.21+</li>
          <li>Especialidad: Survival 1.12.2</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <p>&copy; 2020-2025 QuickLand Network. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
          <p class="mt-1">Minecraft es una marca registrada de Mojang Studios. Este servidor no está afiliado con Mojang Studios.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs">
          <p>Desarrollado con ❤️ para la comunidad de Minecraft</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>